headline: NXP Semiconductors N.V. (NXPI) Slid in Q3 Despite Reporting Results In Line With Expectations
summary: Loomis Sayles, an investment management company, released its “International Growth Fund” third quarter 2024 investor letter. A copy of the letter can be downloaded here. The fund returned 13.10% vs. 8.06% for the MSCI ACWI Ex USA Index (Net) in the quarter. Stock selection in consumer discretionary, information technology, financials, consumer staples, and communication services […]
